      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HUNTERVIEW JACK (4) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (30.24) last time in a Mix at this track. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Can make amends. LADY LLORONA (5) was checked in the run and safely held when fifth (30.67) in a Maiden over 515m at Gosford. Has the ability and can measure up. OTTO MANN (2) has an honest record despite remaining a maiden and is long overdue for a win, having placed five of nine career runs. Has placed at his last two starts now. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Winning chance. ZIPPING NICHOLLS (1) is by Zipping Kyrgios out of Shoshe making debut. Drawn favourably and can capitalise. Market to provide the best guide to his chances.",
